---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="About"
    description="About log.fisher.sh"
    date={new Date('2026-05-30')}
>
    <p>
        This is <strong>log.fisher.sh</strong> — Fisher Evans' writeup of homelab tinkering, on-call incidents
        from the Nottingham cluster, and the engineering decisions behind both. Written when something
        worth recording happens.
    </p>

    <p>
        Stack: <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> for the site, content authored via
        <a href="https://pagescms.org/">Pages CMS</a>, served by Cloudflare Pages, media hosted on
        Cloudflare R2 at <code>media.fisher.sh</code> with offsite backup to Backblaze B2.
    </p>

    <p>
        The source for this site lives at <a href="https://github.com/fisherevans/log">github.com/fisherevans/log</a>.
        The infrastructure it depends on (and most of the war stories) is documented at
        <a href="https://github.com/fisherevans/nottingham-cloud">github.com/fisherevans/nottingham-cloud</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Reach me: <a href="mailto:fisher@fisherevans.com">fisher@fisherevans.com</a> ·
        <a href="https://github.com/fisherevans">github.com/fisherevans</a>.
    </p>
</Layout>
